Zijes pre pritomnost a pre buducnost. Ale ak ta to fakt trapi, tak zajdi za
psychiatrom (mzno by stacil aj psycholog). Neviem, ci by ti pomohlo, ak by si
sa vyspovedal fararovi, no ale skusit to mozes, naber odvahu a ides. Sak vies
kolko roznych spovedi si on uz vypocul?
